{"text_id":64273,"tokens":["This"," paper"," investigates"," the"," spectral"," efficiency"," of"," spectrum"," pooling"," systems",","," where"," multiple"," coherent"," signals"," are"," combined"," and"," transmitted"," over"," a"," shared"," medium","."," Our"," motivation"," stems"," from"," the"," need"," to"," improve"," signal"," quality"," in"," decentralized"," wireless"," networks"," where"," efficient"," use"," of"," the"," frequency"," spectrum"," is"," crucial","."," We"," delve"," into"," the"," mathematical"," framework"," of"," spectral"," efficiency",","," considering"," factors"," such"," as"," signal"," correlation",","," pool"," size",","," and"," interference"," levels","."," Our"," approach"," employs"," analytical"," modeling"," and"," numerical"," simulations"," to"," assess"," the"," performance"," of"," spectrum"," pooling"," systems"," under"," different"," operating"," conditions","."," Results"," reveal"," significant"," enhancements"," in"," spectral"," efficiency"," compared"," to"," conventional"," direct"," transmission",","," particularly"," when"," dealing"," with"," correlated"," signals"," and"," limited"," pool"," sizes","."," We"," establish"," analytical"," bounds"," on"," achievable"," spectral"," efficiency"," and"," identify"," key"," design"," parameters"," that"," impact"," system"," performance","."," Our"," findings"," provide"," valuable"," insights"," into"," the"," optimization"," of"," spectrum"," utilization"," for"," spectrum"," pooling"," systems"," in"," various"," applications",","," including"," multi","-","user"," communication",","," cognitive"," radio",","," and"," sensor"," networks","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gemma-7b-it","label":1}